comments.body: I don't know much about the domain name industry, but I've met a lot of interesting people at the domain summit in London, which happens each year. This year, it's in August, and here's another chance for you to be part of this amazing event. I see that you have a really big portfolio. Maybe you need to find some brokers or something like that. I would suggest coming to an event like this or even going on stage to represent what you have. I think you could find some interesting investors.https://www.dnforum.com/threads/london-domain-summit-2024-preliminary-dates-tickets-sponsorships-gala-and-more.608237/
